---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Navigation from '../components/Navigation.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="London City FC - Stadium"
  description="Maurice Rebak Stadium - The official home of London City Football Club"
>
  <Navigation />
  
  <!-- Hero Section -->
  <section class="hero">
    <img src="/images/stadium 1.jpeg" alt="Maurice Rebak Stadium" class="hero-image" loading="eager" />
    <div class="hero-overlay"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="hero-content">
        <h1 class="hero-title">Maurice Rebak Stadium</h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">Our Home Ground</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Main Content -->
  <main class="main-content">
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container">
        <div class="section-content">
          <p class="lead-text">
            The Maurice Rebak Stadium is the official home of London City Football Club.
          </p>
          <p>
            We are proud to announce Maurice Rebak Stadium as our home ground — a venue that perfectly reflects the ambition, professionalism, and long-term vision of our project.
          </p>
          
          <div class="image-container">
            <img src="/images/stadium 2.jpeg" alt="Maurice Rebak Stadium" class="content-image" loading="lazy" />
          </div>

          <p>
            Located approximately 35–40 minutes from central London, the stadium is easily accessible by public transport and road, making it convenient for supporters, partners, and visiting teams alike.
          </p>

          <p>
            With a capacity of around 3,000 spectators, covered stands, excellent pitch conditions, and modern facilities, Maurice Rebak Stadium is widely recognised as one of the finest non-league stadiums in London. The venue also benefits from ample parking, hospitality areas, and a matchday environment that delivers a true football experience.
          </p>

          <div class="image-grid">
            <img src="/images/stadium 3.jpeg" alt="Stadium facilities" loading="lazy" />
            <img src="/images/stadium 1.jpeg" alt="Stadium atmosphere" loading="lazy" />
          </div>

          <p>
            More than just a stadium, this venue gives London City Football Club a strong sense of identity and credibility. It underlines the seriousness of our project and provides the ideal platform to grow our fanbase, attract partners, and build a club capable of progressing through the English football pyramid.
          </p>

          <p class="emphasis-text">
            Maurice Rebak Stadium is not only our home — it is where our journey begins.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
